    "gp_section_598005407789351479": {
      "type": "gp-section-598005407789351479",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "d0f52913fd63b27b084cab5b4befd4d938280632f4ba0ede21bf375389bb1565_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggGkzemG1js_text": "<span style=\"color:#055BDC;\"><strong>Imagine Waking Up Tomorrow Without That First Jolt of Pain</strong></span>",
        "ggWQIG9fsLw_text": "Your Spine Is Literally Suffocating – And Pills Won’t Save It",
        "ggN5O792d2I_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggN5O792d2I_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggN5O792d2I_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/240ec8e538074993b7ead7f902e0f92c.mp4",
        "ggN5O792d2I_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/Screenshot_11.webp",
        "ggymlr3ksYA_text": "Your Spine Is Literally Suffocating – And Pills Won’t Save It",
        "ggj3LHKR5Jp_text": "<p>Here’s what nobody tells you about chronic back pain and sciatica:</p>",
        "gg4YoJ0BCta_text": "<p>It’s not about your muscles. It’s not about your posture. It’s not even about inflammation.</p>",
        "ggQAm8x-ujQ_text": "<p>It’s about your spinal discs – the shock absorbers between your vertebrae – slowly dying from dehydration.</p>",
        "ggRTR9XYKM9_text": "<p>Your discs are 80% water. When you’re young, they’re plump, juicy, full of fluid. They keep your vertebrae separated and your nerves happy.</p>",
        "ggWaLe4w3DQ_text": "<p>But after age 30, those discs start losing fluid. Getting thinner. Flatter. Like sponges left in the sun.</p>",
        "gg0045cZav__text": "<p>Your vertebrae crush closer together. The space for your nerves shrinks. And your sciatic nerve? It gets squeezed like a garden hose under a truck tire.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_598005407788892727": {
      "type": "gp-section-598005407788892727",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "1c10402c6786d668b0a59a3c161782bfee8f7dc5726392895ef506e0f92e5489_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggzRfc3KmKh_text": "The SmoothSpine Multi Therapy Pro Rehydrates Spinal Discs &amp; Relieves Sciatic Nerve Pressure",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/73446a4d43364e5e9d60bac080b01ebb.mp4",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/Screenshot_12.webp",
        "ggclZmxOds__text": "The SmoothSpine Multi Therapy Pro Rehydrates Spinal Discs &amp; Relieves Sciatic Nerve Pressure",
        "gg5gEyQLqLG_text": "<p>This isn’t a massage cushion. This isn’t a TENS unit. This is medical-grade spinal decompression.</p>",
        "gg-RifOCijk_text": "<p>Here’s what happens the moment you lie down:</p>",
        "ggu6Yd3u6Yx_text": "<p><strong>Dynamic Air Traction: </strong>Feel that “pop”? Years of compression releasing. Your vertebrae separate 3–7mm. Instant relief as your crushed nerve gets space.</p>",
        "ggyZ6Gf5lWo_text": "<p><strong>Deep Heat Therapy: </strong>122°F heat penetrates while traction continues. Your dried-out discs start absorbing fluid like sponges in water. Shooting pain down your leg? Fading.</p>",
        "ggrYT7cGWvp_text": "<p><strong>Targeted Massage Therapy: </strong>Vibration pulses wake up dormant muscles. Blood floods areas starved of oxygen for years. Inflammation breaks up. Muscles retrain.</p>",
        "ggCBSPKh0Z7_text": "<p><strong>EMS + Red Light Therapy: </strong>Low-frequency pulses strengthen your lumbar support system. 660nm red light reduces inflammation at the cellular level. Everything locks in place.</p>",
        "gg_-bnIX9QK_text": "<p>The best part?</p>",
        "gglNkdnoYHM_text": "<p>You can use it from the comfort of your own home, even in your bed.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_598005407789417015": {
      "type": "gp-section-598005407789417015",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "43dc243cf0556cc71837ae0c85e5681af9cd6359d2b0f8fc05b1eb99bcfd70f6_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg6lqX8ncBw_text": "Grounded in Real Science. Trusted by Professionals.",
        "ggr9awOTvod_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggr9awOTvod_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggr9awOTvod_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/e976535c73d740519639256d89c0667d.mp4",
        "ggr9awOTvod_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/Screenshot_15.webp",
        "ggihisY810h_text": "Grounded in Real Science. Trusted by Professionals.",
        "ggiVlsgDWSA_text": "<p>Physical therapists and spine specialists aren’t always within reach—and a single session can cost $150–$200.</p>",
        "ggTX3oVSncW_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine Multi Therapy Pro was engineered in collaboration with orthopedic surgeons and licensed physical therapists who’ve spent decades treating chronic back pain and sciatica.</p>",
        "ggcllM8jPEK_text": "<p>For less than the cost of a single therapy appointment, you get a medical-grade device that delivers the same decompression, heat, massage, EMS, and red light therapy that clinics charge thousands for.</p>",
        "ggwEJrM_VIv_text": "<p><strong>Clinical Evidence:</strong></p>",
        "gg3LCZKwLyt_text": "<p><strong>Swedish study (1987): </strong>91% of sciatica is disc dehydration</p>",
        "ggUraYE6NrG_text": "<p><strong>Saal &amp; Saal (1989):</strong> Non-surgical decompression = 86% success rate</p>",
        "gg-Z5gRCDvc_text": "<p><strong>Mooney (1990): </strong>Heat therapy increases disc nutrient absorption by 47%</p>",
        "ggEp2TI9fEZ_text": "<p><strong>Hides et al. (1994): </strong>EMS restores muscle function in chronic pain patients</p>",
        "ggKxNI6U9MA_text": "<p><strong>NASA study (2001): </strong>Red light accelerates tissue healing by 40%</p>",
        "gg9L3EDUCMV_text": "The Entire Country Is Raving About the SmoothSpine Multi Therapy Pro",
        "ggW6FuzFFTV_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggW6FuzFFTV_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggW6FuzFFTV_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/cd7d2dc070d54eaaad2fcc53e7a99f7b.mp4",
        "ggW6FuzFFTV_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/Screenshot_13.webp",
        "ggGQXnMY5zT_text": "The Entire Country Is Raving About the SmoothSpine Multi Therapy Pro",
        "ggihBBrHnWy_text": "<p><strong>Users are reporting dramatic improvements after just their first week. And 96% continue using it daily.</strong></p>",
        "ggaFHF5sugD_text": "<p>This means that within days of using the <strong>SmoothSpine Multi Therapy Pro</strong>, you can expect to start noticing:</p>",
        "gg3GwCpV-GT_text": "<p>Freedom from stabbing back pain and shooting leg cramps</p>",
        "gg0znNmAU8T_text": "<p>Improved mobility without bracing for pain</p>",
        "ggOLny2Lf9H_text": "<p>Better sleep—waking up rested instead of stiff</p>",
        "gg8AUpoc7KP_text": "<p>Boosted confidence walking, bending, and standing</p>",
        "ggSvIZrM2QP_text": "<p>The energy to do things you’ve been avoiding for years</p>",
        "ggYhZQDCRPW_text": "<p>In just 15 minutes a day, you can give yourself another shot at a normal, pain-free life.</p>"
      }
    },
