        "ggYQI7MgmIJ_text": "<p>STEP 3: Power On &amp; Customize Your Therapy</p>",
        "ggId2rDtgdA_text": "<p>Your body is unique. Your relief should be too. Customize each Multi Therapy Pro session using the remote.</p>",
        "ggbOeJF8hLi_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggbOeJF8hLi_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggbOeJF8hLi_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/6393d7e393ff48e292088c2e84d5412c.mp4",
        "gg1jsqZY6VL_text": "<p>STEP 4: Feel the Difference Immediately</p>",
        "ggVUrtxKQwR_text": "<p>Most users feel relief during their first session. But real transformation comes with consistency – use it 1–2 times daily for at least 2 weeks.</p>",
        "ggcZ3SpDt7L_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
